      "data": {
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "tutorial-basic-primitives"
        },
        "markdown": "## Declaration\n\nUse `declaration` for the graph handshake.\n\nIt owns three editor sections:\n- `identity`\n- `intent`\n- `declaration`\n\nThose sections answer:\n- what this graph is called\n- what kind of artifact it is\n- what port surfaces it exposes\n\nKey fields to understand:\n- `identity.graphId`\n- `identity.name`\n- `intent.kind`\n- `declaration.defaultSurfaceId`\n- `declaration.surfaces[]`\n\nFor the full field-by-field explanation, open the Declaration Walkthrough.",
        "_placement": {
          "version": 1,
          "state": "manually-shaped",
          "source": "manual",
          "updatedAt": 1780528166028,
          "reason": "node-drag"
        }
      }
    },
